snippet.title: Tom Macdonald - "Dummies" | her habits REACTION!!
snippet.description:
Welcome welcome, it's feels like just yesterday I was reacting to Tom Macdonald's trending hit Brainwashed". It was quite the rap to say the least and Tom Macdonald is already right back at it again with a new song and music video for "Dummies". Hope you enjoy my reaction!
